# GETTUPPENT Project - Claude Code Rules

## Stack
Next.js 14+ | Firebase | Stripe | Three.js | Tailwind | TypeScript

## Principles
- Security-first: validate inputs, check auth, sanitize outputs
- Test-first: write tests before implementation
- Type-safe: strict TypeScript, no `any`

## Skills
Located in `skills/` - use for guidance on best practices.
Key skills: nextjs-best-practices, firebase, stripe-integration, test-driven-development, stitch-react-components

## Structure
- `src/app/` - Pages (App Router)
- `src/components/` - UI components
- `src/lib/` - Utilities & configs
- `skills/` - AI coding skills
